      • createMethodAssertions

        public static void createMethodAssertions(CodeElement codeElement,
                                          TestMethod testMethod)
        Static method to create TestAssertions for the CodeMethods of a given CodeElement and adding them to a given TestMethod.
        Creates TestAssertions for the amount of CodeMethods, whether a CodeMethod is defined, whether the return type of a CodeMethod matches and whether the modifiers of a defined CodeMethod match.
        Parameters:
        codeElement - the CodeElement containing the CodeMethods
        testMethod - the TestMethod to add the created TestAssertions to.
